{
  "texts": [
    "In total, there are 796 instances annotated for cause-effect extraction.",
    "These include both unicausal cases (with an average of 621.67 instances) and multicausal cases (with an average of 174.33 instances).",
    "This task challenges models to handle potentially complex causal chains, where one event can trigger multiple consequences or multiple factors can lead to a single outcome.",
    "FinCausal-SC pushes beyond simple keyword matching toward more nuanced and contextaware understanding of financial news articles.",
    "This dataset is published under the CC0 License."
  ]
}